{"tid":1794553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小心！！屯門市中心csl sales sell手機保險呃9人！！","createTime":"2019-12-23T07:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T04:07:28.000Z","uid":297939,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5aee03f8c8656011422d72bc77da9565f7cae30e","tid":1794553,"uid":297939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的。<br />\n當初7月14號買咗部 iphone xs max，買手機嗰時屯門市中心嗰間csl個sales大大聲拍哂心口咁同我講<br />\n<br />\n話 &lsquo;&rsquo;如果買咗保險，日後手機有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何損壞</span></span>，就算係人為，你突然想換部新嘅手機型號都好，突然睇部手機唔順眼都好，話知你點，總知想要部新機，你掟爛部手機，然後你打翻去呢間保險公司，佢哋就會<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費</span></strong></span>換部同一型號嘅新機比你，如果你想要再新型號嘅機，補翻差價就換到。&lsquo;&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n見咁正，就join咗個plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，月月供$48蚊，到目前為止都供咗4個月，綁定供2年。咁就仆街了。<br />\n<br />\n小妹近排部手機無跌嘅情況下端端壞咗開唔到機，就打去保險公司諗住換部新機，再理想啲打算換部iphone  11。<br />\n<br />\n點知保險公司同我講話要我比多3千幾蚊先換到部新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，話合約寫咗&quot;手機/平板電腦建議零售原價的28%&quot;。但csl當時明明講嗰28%係換新型號，貴過原先型號先係要比！csl個sales完全冇講過要比錢換同一型號嘅新機！！公司負責人話叫我打去csl問，依家都仲未有回覆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂，你哋講嘅野有出入喎！！咁去誤導消費者都有？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初講話免費就換到新機依家又話要比錢？我要比多3千幾蚊先換到部新咁我join個plan嚟托7呀？我仲要繼續供2年！下下部機有事即刻我買咗保險都要額外比錢，每次比3千幾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我倒不如直接拎部機去apple整又或者直接拎啲錢去買部新機啦，買保險嚟做乜9？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我依家cut個plan又會被告毀約，我可以點？告消委會告唔告得入？"},{"pid":"65cd4b6d23e4b752b824a4b5e4f384ed0746a7e6","tid":1794553,"uid":297939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:02:14.000Z","msg":"沉得太快 推！！"},{"pid":"2634d57fd681c79241d8027fa3b8e4e06511e8d7","tid":1794553,"uid":46595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:02:20.000Z","msg":"份約應該白紙黑字你簽左名<br />\n呢個位好難告得入<br />\n除非你證明到佢口頭講過呢D野...例如錄音"},{"pid":"b6c2976fb0bc135905a9cf4432d54b32d6571eea","tid":1794553,"uid":297939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"35e956d0fef72055a2672b432efe0ff51d6b0dd6","tid":1794553,"uid":297939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2634d57fd681c79241d8027fa3b8e4e06511e8d7","tid":1794553,"uid":46595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:02:20.000Z","msg":"份約應該白紙黑字你簽左名<br />\n呢個位好難告得入<br />\n除非你證明到佢口頭講過呢D野...例如錄音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"Csl真係唔係第一次咁奸！<br />\n以前為咗tum我屋企人jo in佢公司，話可以幫我屋企人check到一直用開另一間電訊合約完未，話完咗，點知join咗後，以前用開嗰間電訊就打嚟話我屋企人毀約要賠錢！！"},{"pid":"dee2bc19fd00a3b67c9b27fdb24836188fa80792","tid":1794553,"uid":161498,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"垃圾post 拉"},{"pid":"7f5e4847a6c3c9a1ecaebdc58c1bbc9c142078ea","tid":1794553,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"話明CSL = 痴線撚<br />\n係得你痴線撚先會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so